    loc_chca_intro_01_03 = "O idiota do caralho tava ajudando com a padaria, começou a falar com um policial que tava lá tomando café, disse umas coisas bem idiotas. Agora tô com problemas com esse policial que tá sabendo das coisas.",--Stupid motherfucker was helping in the bakery the other day, starting talking to a cop who was sitting there drinking coffee, saying some very stupid things. Now I have this problem with the cop who knows shit.
    loc_chca_intro_01_04 = "O que isso tem a ver com o assalto?",--What does this have to do with the heist?
    loc_chca_intro_01_05 = "Eu sei lá! A gente tá sentado aqui esperando. Só queria quebrar o gelo.",--I don't know! We're just sitting here waiting. I was just making conversation.
    loc_chca_intro_01_07 = "Então, o que você acha que deveria fazer?",--So what do you think I should do?
    loc_chca_intro_01_08 = "Como eu deveria saber, seu burro do caralho!",--How the blerrie hell should I know, you dwankie!
